objectives_summary: This course is going to give you clear, simple steps to follow that will feel easy and natural and will allow you to finally attract unlimited wealth that you want into your life. There are many guided visualizations, meditations and NLP techniques used throughout the course which reprogramme your Sub-Conscious Mind to attract wealth. All of our deep seated beliefs about money are stored in our subconscious mind and influence every decision we make. To change our wealth reality we have to pacify all the inner objections or beliefs which stop us from moving forward. The course comprises of 11 videos, which are a mixture of video, visualisation sessions, practical activities and written work. After you complete each module and go through the simple activities, you will see a huge transformation in the way you think about money, the way you feel and the way you behave around money.  I’ll teach you how to change your entire mind set about wealth so that you are ready to allow more money, wealth and abundance into your life.
